  • Field Details

    • allControllers

      protected static final BaseController[] allControllers
      This is the meta registrar of controllers. This is to prevent two different controller types from existing on the same channel and to reduce memory impact by reducing redundant objects. To use, simply query the index corresponding to the port desired and if null, create and set. Otherwise, verify controller type then use.
      See Also:
      createOrGet(int, Controllers)
